data.meta_description: During her official visit to Copenhagen in Denmark, Roberta METSOLA, EP President meets with Lars Løkke RASMUSSEN, Danish Minister for Foreign Affairs and Mette FREDERIKSEN, Danish Prime Minister. Later on, she participates to the "Joint Event ‘Europe, what next? Dealing with dilemmas from Climate to War and Migration". Extracts from the meetings and from the event.
